About
Manatee's Tiki Bar
Manatee’s Tiki Bar, located poolside at Wyndham Garden Fort Walton Beach on Okaloosa Island, offers a laid-back island vibe with delicious food, refreshing drinks, and daily happy hour specials. Join us for the ultimate tropical experience with burgers, cocktails, and more!

Frequently Asked Questions
The Manatee's FAQ
Where is Manatee’s Tiki Bar located?
Manatee’s Tiki Bar is located poolside at Wyndham Garden Fort Walton Beach on Okaloosa Island, making it the perfect spot to enjoy great food and drinks with a view.
What type of food does Manatee’s Tiki Bar serve?
We serve delicious burgers, chicken wings, sandwiches, appetizers, and baskets, crafted with fresh ingredients to satisfy all your poolside cravings.
What drinks are available at the bar?
Our bar features frozen cocktails, signature margaritas, ice-cold beers, and a wide selection of drinks from our full bar menu.
Does Manatee’s Tiki Bar have a happy hour?
Yes! We offer a daily happy hour with special prices on select drinks. Visit us to unwind and enjoy the best poolside deals on Okaloosa Island.
Can I bring my kids to Manatee’s Tiki Bar?
Absolutely! Manatee’s Tiki Bar is family-friendly, offering delicious food and a welcoming atmosphere for guests of all ages.
Do you offer takeout or delivery?
Currently, we offer takeout for your convenience. Enjoy your favorite Manatee’s Tiki Bar food and drinks wherever you like!
Are there vegetarian options on the menu?
Yes, we have a selection of items that cater to vegetarians. Ask our staff for recommendations, and we’ll help you find something delicious!
Is there outdoor seating available?
Yes, Manatee’s Tiki Bar offers plenty of outdoor seating by the pool, allowing you to enjoy your food and drinks in a relaxed, open-air setting.
What are your hours of operation?
Our hours may vary seasonally. Please check our website or social media for the most up-to-date hours of operation.
How can I contact Manatee’s Tiki Bar?
You can reach us through the contact form on our website or by calling Wyndham Garden Fort Walton Beach. We’re happy to assist you!
